title: About
text: I am Zi Xin, a year 1 freshie studying Industrial Design and I have a strong passion for UX/UI. In my free time, I enjoy playing sports and solving puzzles. I like keeping myself busy but also enjoy slow paced moments. I am taking this module as part of my minor, Interactive Media Development. Here are all the files I have from week 1 to 9.
